data.text:
Cypher has 397 quotes.

A downloadable folder containing all the audio files on this page can be found here.

Agent Select and Abilities[]

Pick agent[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherPick.mp3 "Nothing stays hidden from me. Nothing."

Trapwire[]

Destroyed[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTrapwireDestroyed1.mp3 "They found my wire."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTrapwireDestroyed2.mp3 "Tripwire destroyed."

Triggered[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTrapwireTriggered1.mp3 "Caught one!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTrapwireTriggered2.mp3 "Found you."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTrapwireTriggered3.mp3 "Careful now."

Cyber Cage[]

Activate[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherCyberCageActivate.mp3 "Cage triggered."

Spycam[]

Mark enemy[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamMark1.mp3 "Got you."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamMark2.mp3 "Tagged."

Destroyed[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamDestroyed1.mp3 "Camera taken out."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamDestroyed2.mp3 "Camera taken out."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamDestroyed3.mp3 "My camera is destroyed."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSpycamDestroyed4.mp3 "Ah, my eyes are down."

Utility[]

Place during buy phase[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherPlaceUtility1.mp3 "Oh, this is a nice spot!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherPlaceUtility2.mp3 "Yes, this should do."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherPlaceUtility3.mp3 "This goes here."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherPlaceUtility4.mp3 "That goes there."

Neural Theft[]

Ally Cast[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherUltAllyCast.mp3 "Where is everyone hiding?"

Enemy Cast[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherUltEnemyCast.mp3 "I know exactly where you are!"

Unviable target[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherUltUnviable.mp3 "Give me a corpse!"

Resurrected[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherResurrect.mp3 "For a moment, I saw them!"

Buy Phase[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart1.mp3 "They're scared. I don't need cameras to see that."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart2.mp3 "Nobody escapes me. But they'll try."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart3.mp3 "I wonder if they have any parts I can salvage. Hmm, implants? I need those!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart4.mp3 "Ah, okay, this is good! I've got new gadgets to try out."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart5.mp3 "I must survive to protect my family. I can't lose them. I can't feel that pain again."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart6.mp3 "Let's see what I have to use. Pictures of their children? Wow, way too dark."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart7.mp3 "I will stop anyone who tries to come through. I must keep my secrets with me."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart8.mp3 "The back alleys, or the streets of war. There is no difference. Just nicer toys."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStart9.mp3 "I'm prepared to die for this mission, though I'd really rather not."

On Attack[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartAttack1.mp3 "It's decided. Their radianite belongs to us, you see? No ethical dilemma. مش مُشكِل."

(مش مُشكِل: No problem)

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartAttack2.mp3 "Think of it this way. The more radianite we take from them, the less I borrow from all of you. Extra incentive."

On Defense[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartDefense1.mp3 "These impostors threaten everything! Nora, نقدرش نخليهم يخسروا الغزال ديالي."

(نقدرش نخليهم يخسروا الغزال ديالي: I can't let them destroy my beloved)

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartDefense2.mp3 "I detect an incursion into our world? Hah, no, the other team is just very noisy!"

Bind[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartBind.mp3 "What has Kingdom done to this town?! However pretty their lies are, they're just sucking my city dry!"

Fracture[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartFracture.mp3 "Imagine all the information once kept here, lost in seconds! Ah, خسارة!"

(خسارة: What a loss!)

Split[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchStartSplit.mp3 "Ah, I've always wanted to pry my way in here. Don't mind if I just leave some... gifts behind."

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart1.mp3 "They're usually distracted once I reveal them. Make sure you take advantage."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart2.mp3 "Where will they go this time?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart3.mp3 "One of my cameras is broken!- Oh, wait, okay. It's fine."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart4.mp3 "They will scurry, and then they will die."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart5.mp3 "I can't see them yet. But I can feel them getting ready."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart6.mp3 "Give me a moment. I need to set back up."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart7.mp3 "If they try something, I'll see it."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart8.mp3 "Will they try the same old tricks?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart9.mp3 "We know more than we did before. Let's use that."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart10.mp3 "I find them, I kill them. Simple as that."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundStart11.mp3 "Now remember, wipe the prints from your guns. It's just good crime scene etiquette."

Last round won[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundWon1.mp3 "They're on the back foot, let's deliver another blow!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundWon2.mp3 "An injured dog bites hard. Careful."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundWon3.mp3 "Good work, friends! Keep using my vision to your advantage."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRoundWon4.mp3 "Find them again. Kill them again."

Last round won while in the lead[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLead1.mp3 "We're doing good. Let's do better. Just for fun."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLead2.mp3 "Blink, and they'll catch up. Stay alert."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLead3.mp3 "Wonderful! It's great to see how frightened they are."

Making a comeback[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherComeback1.mp3 "Let us use our sight to our advantage."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherComeback2.mp3 "Don't worry. The house always wins."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherComeback3.mp3 "Their confidence begins to crack. أنا شفته, ah, I can see it."

(أنا شفته: I saw it)

Last round in the half[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastRound1.mp3 "We lose all our money after this. Might as well use it."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastRound2.mp3 "Spend like there is no tomorrow! Because there just might not be."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastRound3.mp3 "Nothing will be saved after this. Use it."

Match Point[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchPoint1.mp3 "I saw their desperation. Let's use that."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchPoint2.mp3 "Let's close up shop. I have things to do."

Spike forgotten[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherForgotSpike1.mp3 "Are we going to get the spike?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherForgotSpike2.mp3 "The spike is still in base."

Shop[]

Call for a buy[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBuying1.mp3 "I'm buying."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBuying2.mp3 "I'm buying."

Call for a save[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSaving1.mp3 "I'm saving."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherSaving2.mp3 "I'm saving."

Offer to buy for allies[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherOffer1.mp3 "I have money if you need."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherOffer2.mp3 "I have money if you need."

Request weapon[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRequest1.mp3 "I need this."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRequest2.mp3 "I need this."

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown1.mp3 "They have nowhere to hide."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown2.mp3 "Let me find you again."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown3.mp3 "Don't get cozy."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown4.mp3 "That radianite must be ours!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown5.mp3 "We must keep them out."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown6.mp3 "My eyes will tip the balance."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown7.mp3 "I will find them."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown8.mp3 "Let's knock them down!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown9.mp3 "My intel is their obstacle."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown10.mp3 "They crash against our wall."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown11.mp3 "We must shore up our defenses!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown12.mp3 "I must weave my web better."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown13.mp3 "I will find you."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown14.mp3 "I will find you."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown15.mp3 "Okay. Let's get set up."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown16.mp3 "We, will reveal their secrets."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown17.mp3 "Where are you?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown18.mp3 "Now, where to set up shop?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherBarrierDown19.mp3 "يلا مشينا."

(Hurry, let's go.)

Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill1.mp3 "No hard feelings."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill2.mp3 "Put down."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill3.mp3 "Ouch."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill4.mp3 "Enemy down."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill5.mp3 "Hostile removed."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill6.mp3 "Buried."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill7.mp3 "One down."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill8.mp3 "Foolish."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill9.mp3 "One dead."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill10.mp3 "Goodbye."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill11.mp3 "تهلّى."

(Take care.)

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKill12.mp3 "بالسلامة."

(With care.)

Headshot[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot1.mp3 "Headshot."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot2.mp3 "My eyes are better than yours."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot3.mp3 "Eagle-eyed."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot4.mp3 "Deleted."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot5.mp3 "Trick shot."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherHeadshot6.mp3 "Erased."

Melee[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMeleeKill1.mp3 "Knock knock."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMeleeKill2.mp3 "صاحبي اسكت."

(My friend, be quiet.)

Enemy revealed by utility[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKillRevealed1.mp3 "Only I could see you hide. Don't worry."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKillRevealed2.mp3 "I saw you scurry."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherKillRevealed3.mp3 "You were probably afraid."

Triple[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTriple1.mp3 "Three out of five."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherTriple2.mp3 "Three out of five."

Quadra[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherQuadra1.mp3 "Four out of five."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherQuadra2.mp3 "Four out of five."

Last kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKill1.mp3 "Oops, no one to interrogate!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKill2.mp3 "Squashed the last bug."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKill3.mp3 "Wiped clean."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKill4.mp3 "Okay, time for a break."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKill5.mp3 "Okay, they're dead. Take what's useful."

Last kill melee[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKillMelee1.mp3 "You should have been looking more closely."

Last kill enemy MVP[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKillMVP.mp3 "I am Prometheus! And you are just... a god."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLastKillMVP2.mp3 "I saw your secrets. They made you weak."

One kill remaining (game-mode specific)[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherOneKillLeft1.mp3 "One rat left."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherOneKillLeft2.mp3 "One rat left."

Spike[]

Defuse resumed[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherDefuseResumed1.mp3 "Don't interrupt!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherDefuseResumed2.mp3 "Don't interrupt!"

Defuse time running out[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherDefuseLate1.mp3 "This is no problem."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherDefuseLate2.mp3 "This is no problem."

Defuse successful[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherDefuseComplete1.mp3 "Spike defused."

Round End[]

Ace[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAce1.mp3 "You're dead, and I didn't feel anything. Not even a thrill."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAce2.mp3 "Ah, you forget. I've always been a killer."

Clutch[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherClutch1.mp3 "You copies are nothing."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherClutch2.mp3 "You forget. I always play high stakes."

Flawless or Team Ace[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherFlawless1.mp3 "You guys are so much better than my last team!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherFlawless2.mp3 "They were blind."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherFlawless3.mp3 *laughs* "No one left to send a message? Oh well"

Low HP[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLowHP1.mp3 "Nora, I will see you again."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherLowHP2.mp3 "Ugh, I hate visiting underground doctors."

Thrifty[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherThrifty1.mp3 "I'll try to be even more poor next time. It'll be hard, hmm, but I'll try."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherThrifty2.mp3 "You think I don't know how to get by without money?"

Match End[]

Match Win[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin1.mp3 "Ah, so much learned this day. A victory, on many fronts."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin2.mp3 "Never come back. I will take you apart!"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin3.mp3 "My truths stay hidden for one day more."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin4.mp3 "You're lucky I'm generous. Or else your families would be next."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin5.mp3 "I knew your every move. It was sad watching you scamper."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWin6.mp3 "Back to my workshop. Still much to be done."

Bind[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherMatchWinBind.mp3 "Get out of my city!"

Runner Up (game-mode specific)[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRunnerUp1.mp3 "I say that was a good job."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRunnerUp2.mp3 "That was good. But next time, first place."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherRunnerUp3.mp3 "That was fun! Again?"

Agent-specific interactions[]

Ally Breach[]

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyBreachRoundStart.mp3 "Breach, Breach. I took a servo from your arms, for my tripwire, don't be angry. Breach."

Enemy Breach[]

Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyBreachKill.mp3 "Breach breached, hah."

Enemy Brimstone[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyBrimstoneMatchStart.mp3 "Let me see if I can hack into that Brimstone's bracer. If he's anything like our Brimstone, he won't know how to fix it!" *laughs*

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyBrimstoneBarrierDown.mp3 "Retire their Brimstone."

Ally Chamber[]

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyChamberRoundStart.mp3 "With me, Chamber. Your eyes, my cameras. We make a good team."

Enemy Chamber[]

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyChamberRoundStart.mp3 "Be mindful of their Chamber. He does not miss much."

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyChamberBarrierDown.mp3 "Now where did Chamber build his nest?"

Enemy Cypher[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherMatchStart.mp3 "I honestly don't know who the Cypher on their side is. *sighs* A real mystery."

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherRoundStart.mp3 "Who are you? Copy of me? *laughs* Where did you come from?"

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherBarrierDown.mp3 "Who will see better, Amir?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherBarrierDown2.mp3 "I'll crush your eyes, Amir."

Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherKill.mp3 "أيوه سلام عليك"

(Well then, goodbye!)

Last Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyCypherLastKill.mp3 "There can only be one." *laughs*

Ally Fade[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyFadeMatchStart.mp3 "Ah, Fade, سلام. I would offer you a camera, but your methods for gathering intel are a little less traditional."

(سلام: Greetings)

Chat[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyFadeChat.mp3 "Fade, of all people, you've never asked to see my face."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:FadeAllyCypherChat.mp3 "There are more valuable secrets than the look of someone. Will you share those?"

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyFadeRoundStart.mp3 "Fade, keep those nightmares away from me. I already have bad dreams."

Commend[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyFadeCommend.mp3 *laughs* "معلمه. Who would have thought the nightmare lady would be so scary."

(معلمه: A pro)

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyFadeBarrierDown.mp3 "Fade, leave their brains intact."

Enemy Fade[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyFadeMatchStart.mp3 "Exercise caution around their Fade. Not the type you want to meet in a dark alley."

Last Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyFadeLastKill.mp3 "Now I can rest a little easier."

Ally Jett[]

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyJettBarrierDown.mp3 "Fly, my wind assassin. Do what you do best."

Enemy Jett[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyJettMatchStart.mp3 "That wind girl is so jumpy! So annoying! My poor tripwires."

Last Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyJettLastKill.mp3 "No more running, girl."

Ally Killjoy[]

Chat[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:KilljoyAllyCypherChat.mp3 "Cypher, can you show me round the dark web one of these days?"

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyKilljoyChat.mp3 "Oh, oh dear no sweetheart! We must protect you."

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyKilljoyRoundStart.mp3 "Little engineer! I borrowed one of your transmitters for my camera. I'll pay you back! Probably."

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyKilljoyRoundStart2.mp3 "Killjoy, do you have your soldering iron on you? I want it- um, I me- I mean, I-I need it."

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyKilljoyBarrierDown.mp3 "Let's go, little engineer."

Ally Omen[]

Match Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyOmenMatchStart.mp3 "Omen! I have the information you asked for. But my price! My price hasn't been paid yet."

Enemy Omen[]

Last Kill[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherEnemyOmenLastKill.mp3 "Goodbye to you, and your secrets."

Ally Phoenix[]

Round Start[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyPhoenixRoundStart.mp3 "Phoenix! Our little star, keep that furnace burning, okay?"

Commend[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyPhoenixCommend.mp3 "Phoenix, woah. You are really aggressive, I'm impressed! And a little scared."

Barrier Down[]

https://valorant.fandom.com/wiki/File:CypherAllyPhoenixBarrierDown.mp3 "Go, Phoenix. Burn!"

Enemy Phoenix[]

Kill[]
